      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">16. Indemnification</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">You agree to indemnify MPLS LLC against claims arising from your content, your use of Beacons, your violation of these Terms, or your violation of any third party's rights.</p>

      <!-- ─── 17. GOVERNING LAW ─── -->
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">17. Governing Law</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of Minnesota, United States. Any disputes will be resolved in the courts of Hennepin County, Minnesota.</p>

      <!-- ─── 18. CHANGES ─── -->
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">18. Changes to These Terms</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We will notify registered users via email and in-app notification of any material changes to these Terms at least 30 days before they take effect. Continued use after the notice period constitutes acceptance.</p>

      <!-- ─── 19. CONTACT ─── -->
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">19. Contact</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Terms &amp; legal: <a href="mailto:legal@mp.ls" class="text-egyptianBlue underline">legal@mp.ls</a><br>
        Privacy: <a href="mailto:privacy@sojorn.net" class="text-egyptianBlue underline">privacy@sojorn.net</a><br>
